title: 01/04/22 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 01/04/22 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, Chris Simms joins the show and discusses some doubts that he has with the Packers going into the Playoffs. Rick Stroud of the Tampa Bay Times explains why the Bucs have yet to release AB. And Albert Breer looks at the Quarterback Carousel going into this off season. Where could Aaron Rodgers and Baker Mayfield land?
